node.text:
And this post from my husband PK (although it made me cry like a baby) ☺️😭 is just one of the many reasons why I feel so blessed, grateful, and happy today. 🙏🏼 I love you so much buba ❤️ Thank you for making every moment count, for loving me the way you do, for understanding me like nobody else, for letting me be long winded (sometimes) 😂 and for supporting me no matter what. As long as I have you and the munchkins with me, I’m as fulfilled as I can ever be. 🎂🎉❤️ 
#repost @paul_kemsley_pk
・・・
It’s such a strange dilemma for me when we are so public and I question what have the world not seen ? So I decided to show everyone the love we have always had well before #rhobh well before we went on our crazy Hollywood journey , but not before our Jagger ( slightly before our Phoenix ) every word I said at our wedding remains true , maybe it’s understated ... your the very best human being I know and I love you till the end and beyond ... happy bday baby @doritkemsley ❤️

node.text: Phoenix Nava, you are the most incredible little girl filled with a heart of gold and infinite capabilities! I’m so, so proud of the kind, caring nature you possess and yet the first to protect and stand up for those you love(particularly your big brother!) Your sense of humor, charm, curiosity and girlie nature combined with your fearless sense of being is what makes you so lovable and so much fun!! I love you so much my beautiful girl. Can’t wait to celebrate you all week!! 🥳💕😘🎉🎁🎈✨🎂

node.title: Happy 5th birthday to my beautiful, kind, loving, sweet Princess P!!! 🥳💕
